channel.title: MakerGirl
channel.description: MakerGirl is a program led by University of Illinois students that educates 7-10 year old girls on STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics) fields through 3-D printing workshops at the College of Business MakerLab, creative activities, and lessons on leading women in STEM fields.

item.title: Hello, World!
item.description: I have gone back and forth trying to decide whether I should continue this website or not. There were so many questions going inside my head for the past few days. Will this be worth it? What will people say? Do I really have the time for this? In the end, I just decided to continue and be ready to face all the challenges that will come with it. So, here it is. Welcome to my new website, josephmilla.com!
